{"tid":2085004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[最後兩日] 7·1，把握好聽日最後一日可以說服身邊朋友一齊出嘅機會","createTime":"2020-06-29T15:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T19:46:00.000Z","uid":38563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"402c7f5f58d6865cc56e2df1f4219c7092627548","tid":2085004,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[倒數一星期] 7&middot;1，氣勢決定200萬or 20萬人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2077059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2077059</a><br />\n<br />\n[倒數6日] 7&middot;1，遊行表達對政府不滿係香港傳統<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2078603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2078603</a><br />\n<br />\n[倒數5日] 7&middot;1，出就係出 唔出就係唔出，無中立之分<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2080003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2080003</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n喜見今日下午2-6洗版式一人一個7.1 post，至少我相信有份開post嘅你哋到時一定會出嚟，連登並唔係冇凝聚力<br />\n<br />\n2020年7.1，可能真係我哋最後一次風險較低嘅遊行，幻想下往後仲有邊一日行動可以低風險過71？<br />\n<br />\n最後，把握好機會說服身邊朋友，一齊食飯嘅同事<br />\n聽日係最後一日你可以游說到佢出定唔出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WLEDdKd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWLEDdKd.jpg&h=2e74c0c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EzgU8fL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzgU8fL.jpg&h=6f432e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/waOzY4Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwaOzY4Y.jpg&h=2bb658c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sy62owH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSy62owH.jpg&h=f6f16572&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGGFjnm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGGFjnm.jpg&h=352961d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0M2oEA.jpg\" data-thumbnai